        <description>Ably .NET library to enable push notifications on Android devices. This package provides Android-specific push notification functionality using Firebase Cloud Messaging for the Ably realtime messaging platform.</description>
        <releaseNotes>https://github.com/ably/ably-dotnet/releases</releaseNotes>
        <copyright>©2025 Ably Real-time Ltd</copyright>
        <tags>ably realtime messaging push notifications android xamarin firebase fcm mobile websocket pubsub</tags>
